0.dialouge: Can you just leave me alone.

1.dialouge: I practiced hard. I worked hard. I already think enough about the selection without you buzzing in my ear.

3.dialouge: You call me whenever you want, saying whatever you want. But the moment I try to tell you that you're making things worse, you pull out all kinds of excuses.

5.dialouge: "Oh Klay, you've got to be more respectful!"

6.dialouge: "Oh Klay, you're turning our discussion into a debate! I just want to talk."

7.dialouge: Have you ever thought about how your yapping affects me?

8.dialouge: Have you ever shown me any respect?

9.dialouge: Is it that hard to wrap your head around the idea that I don't want to have a discussion.

10.dialouge: Your a coward and the closest you've ever come to apoligizing is "Oh, Klay I can't help it."

11.dialouge: Saying that doesn't help anything. It doesn't make things better.

13.dialouge: I don't care whether you have good intentions or not. You've made this week into a living hell.

14.dialouge: You make me hate the selection mom. You make me hate being a member of the vanguard.

16.dialouge: I'm going to hang up now.

17.dialouge: And try my hardest to pass the selection.
